00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:02,520
 That's what we're gonna be celebrating on Wednesday.

517
00:25:02,520 --> 00:25:05,080
 That should be driving everything we think about

518
00:25:05,080 --> 00:25:06,800
 as we go through this season

