00:25:11,760 --> 00:25:15,560
 something given so that everybody else can receive.

522
00:25:15,560 --> 00:25:17,160
 And if you look through the Christmas story,

523
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:19,620
 it's a story of agape love.

524
00:25:19,620 --> 00:25:21,600
 I mean, think about Mary and Joseph

525
00:25:21,600 --> 00:25:24,560
 who had to sacrifice their reputation

