00:25:24,560 --> 00:25:26,200
 and what everybody else thought of them

527
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:28,240
 and all the judgment everybody was making

528
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:30,740
 because they were unmarried and she was pregnant,

529
00:25:30,740 --> 00:25:33,040
 but they were willing to sacrifice it

