00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:36,880
 in obedience to what God had called them to do, agape.

531
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,560
 Think about the shepherds,

532
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:41,480
 the shepherds who are called by the angels in the sky

