00:26:13,040 --> 00:26:18,040
 they were putting their lives at central risk, agape love.

547
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:20,040
 So when we think about Christmas,

548
00:26:20,040 --> 00:26:22,600
 what we should be asking ourselves is,

