00:27:01,560 --> 00:27:02,840
 Does that make sense to you?

569
00:27:02,840 --> 00:27:04,160
 Okay, let me read this to you.

570
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:06,240
 This is 1 Corinthians 13, starting in verse one.

571
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:09,600
 If I speak in the tongues of men and of angels,

572
00:27:09,600 --> 00:27:11,000
 but have not love,

573
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:14,080
 I am only a resounding gong or a clanging cymbal.

